.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你個餐送得快唔係因為外賣仔勤快係因為你好彩<br />\n正常黎講外賣仔得撚閒搞你個餐拿拿林送左佢好過<br />\n仲有個閪袋擺埋d汽水D倒汗水都會搞到你個袋濕左之後穿哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nd客又會以為我玩鳩佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最戇鳩有次拎住兩個餐俾客催<br />\n送完第一單仲要插一單要我去攞<br />\n我同客服講個客催我想轉走張單<br />\n個仆街死都唔撚肯，我嚇佢話我掉低唔送<br />\n佢係唔撚會理我，話鳩知個客死<br />\n結果我死死氣照送俾個客屌到飛起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef29c3dbf58ad3d978c50852ce9f807d827ce2f4","tid":2195401,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"4cc7da995c811fb95e3ba1b7bbde19b1f6cc7473","tid":2195401,"uid":171866,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"416e9ac620f7972935cdf8dafbdb39572f5962d4","tid":2195401,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7a95a06e6478d37ad51b7b001103f8d18417bd6d","tid":2195401,"uid":171866,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T10:16:30.000Z","msg":"咁而家咪一齊玩串個party"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T10:27:39.000Z","msg":"玩啦反正從來都唔叫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T10:33:20.000Z","msg":"劣質支那劣根性就係咁<br />\n只會向自己人打斧頭剝削，而唔係諗方法提高員工動力增加效率去盈利"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T10:40:02.000Z","msg":"都要多謝呢班奴隸先會有咁嘅老闆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj